Package Hospital.Exception

Exception Summary
ArgumentConstraintException Thrown when the given argument didn't meet given constraints
ArgumentIsNullException Thrown when a given argument was null.
ArgumentNotAnsweredException Thrown when a required Argument-object was not answered.
CannotChangeException This exception is thrown when an argument is given a value a second time.
CannotDischargeException Thrown when a patient could not be discharged.
CannotDoException Thrown when an action could not be performed.
CannotFindOrderException thrown when an order could not be found
IllegalInfo Thrown when an Info-object was invalid.
IllegalScheduleException Thrown when an illegal schedule was used
IllegalStockTypeException Thrown when an requested stock type does not exist
InvalidDiagnosisException Thrown when a used Diagnosis did not exist or was otherwise invalid.
InvalidPatientException Thrown when a used Patient did not exist or was otherwise invalid.
InvalidTimeException Thrown when a used Time was invalid.
ItemNotFoundException Thrown when an Item was not found.
ItemNotReservedException Thrown when an item was not reserved for use.
ItemTypeNotFoundException Thrown when a requested item type was not found
NeedsExpirationTimeException Thrown when an expiration time was not given
NeedsNoExpirationTimeException Thrown when an expiration time was not needed, but was given
NoOpenedPatientFileException Thrown when a PatientFile was not open when one was needed.
NoPersonWithNameAndRoleException Thrown when a person with given name and role could not be found.
NoSpaceAvailableException Thrown when no space is available in stock for the itens to be added
NotAFactoryException Thrown when a given value was not a Factory when it needed to be one.
NotDoneException Thrown when a command could not be executed
NotEnoughItemsAvailableException Thrown when an item is unavailable.
NotLoggedInException Thrown when an action was tried when the LoginController was not logged in.
OrderUnavailableException Thrown when an order is unavailable
PatientIsCheckedInException Thrown when a Patient is checked in when he/she shouldn't be.
PatientIsDischargedException Thrown when a Patient is not checked in when he/she should be.
SchedulableAlreadyExistsException Thrown when a schedulable object already exists in the world.
ScheduleGroupUnavailable Thrown when an empty group of schedules is given to the scheduler.
SchedulingException Thrown when a an error occurs during scheduling.
StockNotFoundException Thrown when the stock is not available
TreatmentAlreadyAddedException Thrown when it is tried to add a Treatment that is already added.
WrongArgumentListException Thrown when the given argument-list doesn't match the expected one.
WrongTreatmentException Thrown when the wrong Treatment type was used
